## `app/(tabs)/profile.ios.tsx` (iOS — 932 lines)
**Identical logic and JSX to `profile.tsx`** — same component, same API calls, same layout. Only differences:
- `scrollContent` `paddingTop` is `16` (not `Platform.OS === 'android' ? 48 : 16`)
- `SafeAreaView` uses `theme.colors.background` instead of hardcoded `'#FFFFFF'`
- No `Platform` import

