## `app/post-gig.tsx` (793 lines)
A standalone Stack screen (outside tabs). Same form as `index.tsx` client view. On success shows `SuccessModal`, then on close navigates `router.replace('/(tabs)/profile')` with a 300ms timeout. On error shows `ErrorModal`. Has `mountedRef` and `navigationTimeoutRef` cleanup. `Stack.Screen` sets `title: 'Post a Gig'` but `_layout.tsx` overrides it with `headerShown: false` for the `post-gig` route.

